RoutingInfo.AdditionalInformation:
THACA broadcasts PLMN 52099 (RAN only) as per GSM standard, PLMN 52004 and 52019 (MOCN) as per UMTS, and PLMN 52004 as per LTE/NR standard and all inbound roamers can be registered. For outbound roamers will only use the 52004 IMSI range.
Roaming partners preferring to roam on True Move H Universal Communication (THACA) must populate PLMN code 52004 (TRUE-H) and 52099 (TRUE-H) and 52019 in their preferred PLMN list in the USIM and SIM.
